Dialogue: ,0:00:02.18,0:00:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;In the daytime, I'm Marinette,{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:00:04.74,0:00:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;just a normal girl with a normal life.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;But there's something about me{\i0}\N{\i1}&lrm;that no-one knows yet{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:00:11.10,0:00:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;because I have a secret.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:00:13.46,0:00:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;♪ Miraculous! Simply the best! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;♪ Up to the test when things go wrong! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:00:18.94,0:00:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;♪ Miraculous! The luckiest! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:00:21.58,0:00:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;♪ The power of love, always so strong! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:00:24.50,0:00:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;♪ Miraculous! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:00:38.58,0:00:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[sigh of relief] That was close.
Dialogue: ,0:00:42.46,0:00:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;What you did for Alya\N&lrm;was very cool, Marinette
Dialogue: ,0:00:46.18,0:00:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You think?\N&lrm;I'd have liked to do more but...
Dialogue: ,0:00:48.82,0:00:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[Sabine] {\i1}&lrm;Marinette, Alya's here!{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:00:50.78,0:00:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[Alya] {\i1}&lrm;Don't worry, I'll just head up.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:00:53.46,0:00:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;She didn't wait long\N&lrm;to tell me the big news.
Dialogue: ,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Hide, Tikki, quick.
Dialogue: ,0:00:59.26,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Girl, you will not believe\N&lrm;what just happened to me!
Dialogue: ,0:01:02.90,0:01:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Ladybug saved some workers\N&lrm;from a villain.
Dialogue: ,0:01:05.66,0:01:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Millions of reporters\N&lrm;were waiting to interview her.
Dialogue: ,0:01:08.94,0:01:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;And that's when it happened!
Dialogue: ,0:01:15.78,0:01:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[reporter]\N{\i1}&lrm;Please, Ladybug, just a few words.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:01:18.98,0:01:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;Hey, are you Alya{\i0}\N{\i1}&lrm;the girl with the blog about me?{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:01:22.22,0:01:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;The Ladyblog?{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:01:23.86,0:01:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;Y-Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;I like your work.{\i0}\N{\i1}&lrm;It's awesome. Keep it up.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:01:27.66,0:01:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;Your earring, Ladybug.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;Thanks. Better get going. Bug out.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:01:33.34,0:01:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;That was super...
Dialogue: ,0:01:34.74,0:01:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Cool, right?
Dialogue: ,0:01:36.10,0:01:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Ladybug knows me. My blog!
Dialogue: ,0:01:38.82,0:01:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;She thinks it's awesome,\N&lrm;awesome!
Dialogue: ,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Yeah, that's... awesome.
Dialogue: ,0:01:44.42,0:01:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Let me grab my laptop.
Dialogue: ,0:01:47.62,0:01:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You're right, Tikki.\N&lrm;I think it made her a little happy.
Dialogue: ,0:01:51.22,0:01:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-Can I see the video?\N&lrm;-OK, but fast.
Dialogue: ,0:01:53.54,0:01:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[she squeals]
Dialogue: ,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You thought I was going to drop it.
Dialogue: ,0:01:59.74,0:02:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[gasping]
Dialogue: ,0:02:00.82,0:02:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[Tikki] Video deleted!
Dialogue: ,0:02:02.42,0:02:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Tell me I didn't just do that.
Dialogue: ,0:02:05.42,0:02:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You didn't just do that.
Dialogue: ,0:02:08.42,0:02:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;OK, you did.\N&lrm;At least you didn't drop it.
Dialogue: ,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I really screwed up this time.
Dialogue: ,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Alya's gonna kill me.
Dialogue: ,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;It's not the end of the world.\N&lrm;Alya will understand.
Dialogue: ,0:02:18.06,0:02:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;She is your best friend.
Dialogue: ,0:02:20.46,0:02:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You're right.
Dialogue: ,0:02:22.30,0:02:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[cheerful muttering]
Dialogue: ,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[growling]
Dialogue: ,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-On second thoughts...\N&lrm;-Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: ,0:02:31.22,0:02:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;To... to a pigeon.
Dialogue: ,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Say hello to Alya, Jacques.
Dialogue: ,0:02:35.06,0:02:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Say bye-bye, Jacques. Come down.
Dialogue: ,0:02:37.14,0:02:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;You've got visitors.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;What's the name of the play is,\N&lrm;Mr. Haprele?
Dialogue: ,0:02:41.78,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;It's...
Dialogue: ,0:02:42.86,0:02:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;It's called, "The Mime's\N&lrm;Extraordinary Adventures"
Dialogue: ,0:02:45.90,0:02:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;starring the most talented\N&lrm;awesome actor and mime.
Dialogue: ,0:02:49.70,0:02:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Come on now...
Dialogue: ,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;My father!
Dialogue: ,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Give it up for Fred Haprele.
Dialogue: ,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Thank you. Thank you, Mylene.
Dialogue: ,0:02:57.18,0:02:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Well, congratulations.\N&lrm;She must be very proud.
Dialogue: ,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;All I need is my hat\N&lrm;to complete my costume.
Dialogue: ,0:03:03.90,0:03:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Here it is.
Dialogue: ,0:03:05.06,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Thank you, Marinette,\N&lrm;saving me at the last minute.
Dialogue: ,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[Marinette giggles]
Dialogue: ,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I don't think\N&lrm;Mylene was exaggerating at all.
Dialogue: ,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Thank you.
Dialogue: ,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I fixed the tear in it.
Dialogue: ,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I also sewed the pocket\N&lrm;on the inside.
Dialogue: ,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;That's perfect.
Dialogue: ,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Thanks to you,
Dialogue: ,0:03:31.26,0:03:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I'll have my good luck charm\N&lrm;with me all the time.
Dialogue: ,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;A photo of my daughter.
Dialogue: ,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Oh, dad.
Dialogue: ,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[phone rings]
Dialogue: ,0:03:40.58,0:03:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Hello...
Dialogue: ,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[shouting] {\i1}&lrm;Where are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-I had to get my hat.\N&lrm;-{\i1}&lrm;I need you now!{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I know.
Dialogue: ,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;The bus leaves in half an hour.\N&lrm;I'll be there.
Dialogue: ,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;That was the play's director.
Dialogue: ,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;She's nervous about the premiere.
Dialogue: ,0:03:53.30,0:03:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;She's ready to blow a fuse.\N&lrm;I better get going.
Dialogue: ,0:03:56.18,0:03:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-See you tonight, girls.\N&lrm;-We can't wait.
Dialogue: ,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Love you, dad.
Dialogue: ,0:04:02.58,0:04:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;What's his excuse this time?
Dialogue: ,0:04:04.54,0:04:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;He said had to get his hat\N&lrm;from a repair shop.
Dialogue: ,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Well, he's a convincing actor.
Dialogue: ,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Actually, he is a great actor,
Dialogue: ,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;but he makes excuses for being late...
Dialogue: ,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;For falling asleep during rehearsals.
Dialogue: ,0:04:17.58,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;for leaving early,
Dialogue: ,0:04:19.02,0:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;for missing parts of his costume.
Dialogue: ,0:04:21.70,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Come on, Sarah,\N&lrm;when are you going to wake up?
Dialogue: ,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;But it's up to you\N&lrm;if you want the show to suffer.
Dialogue: ,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Look, you're his understudy.
Dialogue: ,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Be ready to replace him\N&lrm;just in case, okay?
Dialogue: ,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I won't let you down, Sarah.
Dialogue: ,0:04:34.42,0:04:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Thanks.
Dialogue: ,0:04:36.14,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[he chuckles]
Dialogue: ,0:04:41.70,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Thanks, I gotta go.\N&lrm;I want to change before the show.
Dialogue: ,0:04:45.42,0:04:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[phone rings]\N&lrm;Hey, that's my ringtone.
Dialogue: ,0:04:48.34,0:04:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[Marinette giggles nervously]
Dialogue: ,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Gimme.
Dialogue: ,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;It's my mom, I'll call her back.
Dialogue: ,0:04:56.38,0:04:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Mylene, you wanna see a cool video?
Dialogue: ,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;No!
Dialogue: ,0:05:01.62,0:05:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You wouldn't want her to be late\N&lrm;for her dad's show.
Dialogue: ,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Marinette's right, I gotta go.
Dialogue: ,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;OK, I'll go with you
Dialogue: ,0:05:09.26,0:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;and show you on the way.
Dialogue: ,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Wait, your bag's open.
Dialogue: ,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;All good. See ya.
Dialogue: ,0:05:15.30,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-Bye.\N&lrm;-Bye.
Dialogue: ,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[sigh of relief]
Dialogue: ,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[phone rings]
Dialogue: ,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Sarah, I'm early. I'm around the corner.
Dialogue: ,0:05:26.58,0:05:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;No, it's Chris.
Dialogue: ,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Sarah asked me to call you\N&lrm;about a location change.
Dialogue: ,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;The bus is picking us up\N&lrm;in 10 minutes at the Louvre.
Dialogue: ,0:05:33.98,0:05:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;That's on the other side of town.
Dialogue: ,0:05:36.34,0:05:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Yes, but it's closer\N&lrm;to the Eiffel Tower.
Dialogue: ,0:05:39.30,0:05:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Well... OK.\N&lrm;Luckily, I'll just make it on time.
Dialogue: ,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Thanks for telling me.
Dialogue: ,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Sure, see you there.
Dialogue: ,0:05:47.02,0:05:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[cackling]
Dialogue: ,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[Alya] I'm off this way.
Dialogue: ,0:05:52.82,0:05:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;OK, see you.
Dialogue: ,0:05:53.98,0:05:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Wait, I have to show you\N&lrm;my awesome vid...
Dialogue: ,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Where's my phone?
Dialogue: ,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You stole Alya's phone?
Dialogue: ,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I... I borrowed it.
Dialogue: ,0:06:05.22,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Look, all I need to do is\N&lrm;transform into Ladybug
Dialogue: ,0:06:08.38,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;and film myself doing\N&lrm;the exact same thing.
Dialogue: ,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Then I'll give it back.
Dialogue: ,0:06:13.10,0:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I don't know.\N&lrm;Maybe it's better to come clean now.
Dialogue: ,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You might be digging a bigger hole.
Dialogue: ,0:06:19.06,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I can handle this.
Dialogue: ,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Fine, but don't say I didn't warn you.
Dialogue: ,0:06:23.14,0:06:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[phone vibrates]
Dialogue: ,0:06:25.42,0:06:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-Hi, Mylene.\N&lrm;-{\i1}&lrm;Do you have Alya's phone?{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Alya's phone?
Dialogue: ,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Got it. The silly girl dropped it.
Dialogue: ,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[Alya] {\i1}&lrm;I'm here too.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Hi, Alya. You're on speaker-phone?
Dialogue: ,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;OK, I'll give it to you at the show.
Dialogue: ,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;See ya.
Dialogue: ,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Don't look at me like that.\N&lrm;It'll all work out,
Dialogue: ,0:06:44.82,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I think.
Dialogue: ,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Tikki, spots on!
Dialogue: ,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;We have to go for dress rehearsals.
Dialogue: ,0:07:11.58,0:07:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Wait any longer and you'll be\N&lrm;jeopardising the production.
Dialogue: ,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You're right, Chris. Let's go.
Dialogue: ,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You'll take Fred's place.
Dialogue: ,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I definitely won't let you down.
Dialogue: ,0:07:26.26,0:07:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[panting]
Dialogue: ,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Where are they?
Dialogue: ,0:07:29.86,0:07:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Excuse me, have you seen a bus
Dialogue: ,0:07:31.90,0:07:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;with a poster on it for "The Mime"?
Dialogue: ,0:07:34.94,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[phone vibrates]
Dialogue: ,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;He's got a nerve calling now.
Dialogue: ,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I wouldn't give him the time of day.
Dialogue: ,0:07:42.82,0:07:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-{\i1}&lrm;Sarah, where are you?{\i0}\N&lrm;-You never turned up.
Dialogue: ,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I'm on time... at the Louvre.
Dialogue: ,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;What? Why would we meet there?
Dialogue: ,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I-I thought\N&lrm;the meeting place changed.
Dialogue: ,0:07:53.02,0:07:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Fred, I don't want to hear\N&lrm;you lame excuses.
Dialogue: ,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-But Chris...\N&lrm;-I don't care.
Dialogue: ,0:07:57.34,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;It's not just this excuse,\N&lrm;there's always an excuse.
Dialogue: ,0:08:01.90,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;Enough is enough.{\i0}\N{\i1}&lrm;Chris will be the lead tonight.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;At least I can count on him.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[she sighs]
Dialogue: ,0:08:15.78,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;An actor who misses his premiere.
Dialogue: ,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Now that's a tragedy.
Dialogue: ,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Go, my evil Akuma.
Dialogue: ,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Let's hand this actor\N&lrm;the role of a lifetime!
Dialogue: ,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Okey-dokey, here we go.
Dialogue: ,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[cat meows]
Dialogue: ,0:08:44.58,0:08:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}&lrm;Hey, are you Alya{\i0}\N{\i1}&lrm;the girl with the blog about me?{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:08:48.30,0:08:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[meowing]\N&lrm;Hey! No!
Dialogue: ,0:08:50.02,0:08:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Get away!
Dialogue: ,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;That is so gross.
Dialogue: ,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Cats are nothing but trouble.
Dialogue: ,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[sobbing] What did I do?
Dialogue: ,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You're going to be\N&lrm;so disappointed in me.
Dialogue: ,0:09:04.98,0:09:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Mime,
Dialogue: ,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I am Hawk Moth.
Dialogue: ,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I'm giving you the power
Dialogue: ,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;to make whatever you gesture\N&lrm;come to life.
Dialogue: ,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Destroy this premiere performance.
Dialogue: ,0:09:14.46,0:09:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You may be a mime
Dialogue: ,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;but they can't silence you!
Dialogue: ,0:09:17.94,0:09:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;However, in return,
Dialogue: ,0:09:20.06,0:09:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;you must bring me back Ladybug's\N&lrm;and Cat Noir's Miraculouses.
Dialogue: ,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;So, shall we get on with the show?
Dialogue: ,0:09:29.78,0:09:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[dramatic music]
Dialogue: ,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[clinking]
Dialogue: ,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[he gasps and screams]
Dialogue: ,0:09:47.98,0:09:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[siren wails]
Dialogue: ,0:09:54.98,0:09:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[she gasps]
Dialogue: ,0:10:00.54,0:10:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Are you OK?
Dialogue: ,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Looks like Mylene's dad's hat.
Dialogue: ,0:10:05.78,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[she gasps]
Dialogue: ,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Mr Haprele?
Dialogue: ,0:10:08.54,0:10:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;If you're ticked off.\N&lrm;We can talk about it.
Dialogue: ,0:10:11.74,0:10:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Or not.
Dialogue: ,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[arrows whistle]
Dialogue: ,0:10:17.62,0:10:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[Nathalie] {\i1}&lrm;Yes, sir, understood.{\i0}
Dialogue: ,0:10:19.54,0:10:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I'm sure he'll understand, sir.
Dialogue: ,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;My dad's flaking, isn't he?
Dialogue: ,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Let me guess,\N&lrm;something came up.
Dialogue: ,0:10:26.38,0:10:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Yes, but he reserved\N&lrm;the best seats in the house.
Dialogue: ,0:10:30.30,0:10:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;As usual, the best money can buy.
Dialogue: ,0:10:32.70,0:10:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[gasping]
Dialogue: ,0:10:35.14,0:10:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Get out and hide.
Dialogue: ,0:10:36.58,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I'll cover you.
Dialogue: ,0:10:39.06,0:10:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[romantic music]
Dialogue: ,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[arrows whistle]
Dialogue: ,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;We've gotta transform now.
Dialogue: ,0:10:50.34,0:10:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I thought I was a spectator,\N&lrm;not a performer.
Dialogue: ,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-What about the show?\N&lrm;-No time.
Dialogue: ,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Plagg, claws out!
Dialogue: ,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[clicking]
Dialogue: ,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[clinking]
Dialogue: ,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Grab her Miraculous, her earrings, now!
Dialogue: ,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[rope creaks]
Dialogue: ,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Keep your hands to yourself.
Dialogue: ,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;It's OK, I've got this.
Dialogue: ,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;My pleasure, Cat Noir.
Dialogue: ,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[clinking]
Dialogue: ,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Apparently, not seeing is believing.
Dialogue: ,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;We can't let him go like that.
Dialogue: ,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[bleeping]
Dialogue: ,0:12:00.38,0:12:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[car door opens and shuts]
Dialogue: ,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[car starts]
Dialogue: ,0:12:04.62,0:12:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;No, wait!
Dialogue: ,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-There, I did it.\N&lrm;-I wish you did.
Dialogue: ,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;When he started miming the car,\N&lrm;the bars disappeared.
Dialogue: ,0:12:15.78,0:12:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Hey, wait.
Dialogue: ,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Nice ride\N&lrm;but I'd have made it a convertible.
Dialogue: ,0:12:25.66,0:12:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[car accelerates]
Dialogue: ,0:12:28.98,0:12:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;He's one of the actors\N&lrm;and he's after that bus.
Dialogue: ,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Where is he going?
Dialogue: ,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;We've gotta stop him.
Dialogue: ,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-Hit the brakes.\N&lrm;-What brakes?
Dialogue: ,0:12:39.90,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[screams]
Dialogue: ,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[tires screech]
Dialogue: ,0:12:43.54,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Not bad for driving an invisible car
Dialogue: ,0:12:45.86,0:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;but they'll never believe\N&lrm;we saved their lives.
Dialogue: ,0:12:49.22,0:12:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[clicking]
Dialogue: ,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[motorbike revs up]
Dialogue: ,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;He's off again.
Dialogue: ,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;We've got to catch up with the bus.
Dialogue: ,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;What are you doing?
Dialogue: ,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Good thing you have friends\N&lrm;in high places.
Dialogue: ,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-Hold on.\N&lrm;-I could've done this.
Dialogue: ,0:13:08.22,0:13:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-We're the Cat and Bug team.\N&lrm;-Bug and Cat team.
Dialogue: ,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Drop me off there.
Dialogue: ,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Get ready.
Dialogue: ,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-Where's the Akuma?\N&lrm;-In his hat.
Dialogue: ,0:13:21.06,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-How do you know?\N&lrm;-I have hidden talents.
Dialogue: ,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[engine accelerates]
Dialogue: ,0:13:29.86,0:13:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[dramatic music]
Dialogue: ,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[sword clinks]
Dialogue: ,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-Distract him.\N&lrm;-Gotcha!
Dialogue: ,0:13:37.38,0:13:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Meow.
Dialogue: ,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[he gasps] Fred?
Dialogue: ,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;The Miraculous. Grab her earring!
Dialogue: ,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-Grab his hat.\N&lrm;-Look out!
Dialogue: ,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[chainsaw whirrs]
Dialogue: ,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[grinding]
Dialogue: ,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-We have to get them to safety.\N&lrm;-Can I lend a paw?
Dialogue: ,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Yeah, cover me.
Dialogue: ,0:14:16.86,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Hurry up, Milady.
Dialogue: ,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[tapping]
Dialogue: ,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Stop.
Dialogue: ,0:14:21.78,0:14:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;What's happening?
Dialogue: ,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;An actor has been akumatised,
Dialogue: ,0:14:24.62,0:14:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;and he seems to have it in\N&lrm;for your troupe.
Dialogue: ,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Fred?
Dialogue: ,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[arrows whistle]
Dialogue: ,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[screaming]
Dialogue: ,0:14:48.98,0:14:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Stay inside.
Dialogue: ,0:14:50.58,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;We'll get this under control.
Dialogue: ,0:14:51.98,0:14:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I know why he's after us.\N&lrm;I stole his role
Dialogue: ,0:14:54.82,0:14:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;but he can have it back,\N&lrm;I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: ,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Just keep us safe.
Dialogue: ,0:14:58.58,0:15:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;What do you mean?\N&lrm;You didn't steal it, he lost it.
Dialogue: ,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Not exactly,\N&lrm;I have to tell you something.
Dialogue: ,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;His Miraculous, I want his ring!
Dialogue: ,0:15:35.14,0:15:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I don't know why you're so violent
Dialogue: ,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;but I don't think Mylene would approve.
Dialogue: ,0:15:43.06,0:15:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[bleep]
Dialogue: ,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;That's what I call "silent but deadly".
Dialogue: ,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Lucky charm!
Dialogue: ,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;A shoe box? Great.
Dialogue: ,0:16:02.82,0:16:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;There better be explosive boots in there.
Dialogue: ,0:16:13.62,0:16:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Of course,
Dialogue: ,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;we have to make him really angry.
Dialogue: ,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Blow his fuse!
Dialogue: ,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Isn't he angry enough?
Dialogue: ,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You're good at annoying people.\N&lrm;Do your thing.
Dialogue: ,0:16:23.58,0:16:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Hey...
Dialogue: ,0:16:24.82,0:16:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;That is true.
Dialogue: ,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Gotta borrow these.
Dialogue: ,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;A box, a magnifying glass,
Dialogue: ,0:16:31.58,0:16:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;some light, and voilà!
Dialogue: ,0:16:33.42,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;A homemade projector. Hey, Mime!
Dialogue: ,0:16:35.50,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Nice poster, don't you think?
Dialogue: ,0:17:00.42,0:17:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[screaming]
Dialogue: ,0:17:12.82,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Yes! Remember he can only mime\N&lrm;one thing at a time.
Dialogue: ,0:17:16.02,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;So he's cornered.\N&lrm;Good thinking, Milady.
Dialogue: ,0:17:19.50,0:17:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Thanks.
Dialogue: ,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;No more evil-doing for you, Akuma.
Dialogue: ,0:17:35.34,0:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Time to de-evilise.
Dialogue: ,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Gotcha!
Dialogue: ,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Bye-bye, little butterfly.
Dialogue: ,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Miraculous Ladybug!
Dialogue: ,0:17:52.06,0:17:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[he gasps] Yes!
Dialogue: ,0:17:57.74,0:18:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;What happened? How did I get here?
Dialogue: ,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;POUND IT!
Dialogue: ,0:18:02.78,0:18:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I'm sorry I didn't believe you.
Dialogue: ,0:18:04.82,0:18:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I'm sorry too.
Dialogue: ,0:18:05.98,0:18:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I was so desperate to perform\N&lrm;that I lied to you.
Dialogue: ,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[bleeping] Your earrings.
Dialogue: ,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Better get going.
Dialogue: ,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Shame, I could have been\N&lrm;your date to the play.
Dialogue: ,0:18:19.50,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;-Just you and me.\N&lrm;-Thanks, but I have other plans.
Dialogue: ,0:18:32.02,0:18:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;The show's not over yet, Ladybug.\N&lrm;You just wait.
Dialogue: ,0:18:35.38,0:18:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;There's still a last act to come\N&lrm;when you least expect it.
Dialogue: ,0:18:49.90,0:18:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Got it!
Dialogue: ,0:18:57.94,0:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[Adrien] Hey.
Dialogue: ,0:18:59.06,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;You're here, cool.
Dialogue: ,0:19:00.54,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I thought I'd end up alone.
Dialogue: ,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[Alya] Did you bring my phone?
Dialogue: ,0:19:07.74,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[cheering]
Dialogue: ,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I don't know which I liked more,\N&lrm;the show or Adrien.
Dialogue: ,0:19:21.46,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Give him a call\N&lrm;and ask him out to a movie.
Dialogue: ,0:19:24.34,0:19:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Speaking of calling\N&lrm;I've something to tell you.
Dialogue: ,0:19:28.50,0:19:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I... accidentally erased\N&lrm;your Ladybug video,
Dialogue: ,0:19:31.46,0:19:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;then I dropped your phone in a bin,
Dialogue: ,0:19:34.38,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;and now it stinks,\N&lrm;like really really bad...
Dialogue: ,0:19:38.06,0:19:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;and I'm sorry, so so sorry.
Dialogue: ,0:19:41.22,0:19:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I know that video meant a lot.
Dialogue: ,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I'm a lame friend.
Dialogue: ,0:19:44.94,0:19:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;[she giggles] Chillax, lady.
Dialogue: ,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;If anyone knows\N&lrm;about your legendary clumsiness,
Dialogue: ,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;it's me, your BFF.
Dialogue: ,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;So... You're not angry?
Dialogue: ,0:19:55.54,0:20:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Well... you should have come clean\N&lrm;and told me, but no, we're cool.
Dialogue: ,0:20:00.78,0:20:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Besides, I'd already uploaded it\N&lrm;to my blog.
Dialogue: ,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;I'm so lucky\N&lrm;to have a friend like you.
Dialogue: ,0:20:06.02,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;So you probably don't care\N&lrm;about my surprise.
Dialogue: ,0:20:10.42,0:20:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Screw up or no screw up,\N&lrm;you know I love surprises.
Dialogue: ,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&lrm;Ok. You see that theatre?
